BUSINESS RULE SPECIFICATIONS

RULE INFORMATION

Statement:  If a customer has not made a purchase for a few years, they are marked as inactive.

Constraint: If the last transaction record associated with a given customer is more than 2 years in the past, CustomerIsActive is marked as false

